article_title: Boy who lost legs swims with Winter the dolphin
article_text: Cieran Kelso shares a special bond with Winter, the dolphin who inspired 'Dolphin Tale.' The 8-year-old boy lost his legs to meningitis and uses prosthetic flippers to swim. He flew all the way from England to Florida to swim with Winter.
